* Allows attackers to gain unauthorized access by taking over legitimate accounts
* Caused by easy to guess security questions, implementation flaws, lack of throttling, sending original passwords
* Mitigations include validating input, strong questions, throttling guesses, controlling email destinations, temporary passwords
